[06/01/2019 21:42:19] <font color="#ffffff">Una cascada del Khumbu</font>
[06/01/2019 21:42:19] <font color="#ffffff">que nace a 5350 metros</font>
[06/01/2019 21:42:24] <font color="#ffffff">y acaba alos 6000 metros</font>
