[06/01/2019 21:43:06] <font color="#ffffff">al inicio</font>
[06/01/2019 21:43:06] <font color="#ffffff">dela cascada del Khumbu".</font>
[06/01/2019 21:43:09] <font color="#ffffff">“Un laberinto</font>
[06/01/2019 21:43:09] <font color="#ffffff">de 12 kilómetros de hielo</font>
